---
By: Elaine Hibbard
Locus:
  Page: 207
  Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Gratitude
---
Gratitude is one of the great positive emotions because it creates
magnetism. ...A magnet is that which draws things to itself; therefore, by
giving heartfelt thanks for all the good we now have, through the magnetism
that gratitude creates, we will start attracting more good into our daily
life.
